definitions.definition: Synonym of reverberant ( “ that tends to reverberate (“( repeatedly ) bounce against one or more surfaces ”) or has reverberated ” ) ; re-echoed .
Ringing or vibrating with many echoing sounds ; re-echoing, resounding , reverberating.
